------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                EVALUATING EXPRESSIONS AND OPERATOR PRECEDENCE
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Java expressions are evaluated in the same way as arithmetic expressions.

	ยง Multiplication, divison, and remainder operators are applied first.
	ยง Addition and substraction are applied last.

EXAMPLE: FahrenheitToCelcius.java

You can invoke System.currentTimeMillis() to return the current time.

The currentTimeMillis method is the System class returns the current time in milliseconds elapsed since the
time midnight, January 1, 1970 GMT.

EXAMPLE: ShowCurrentTime.java


